title: Switzerland Employment Change
description: Employment in Switzerland increased by 0.20 in June of 2022. Employment Change in Switzerland averaged 0.26 percent from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1.20 percent in the first quarter of 2011 and a record low of -2.10 percent in the second quarter of 2020. This page provides - Switzerland Employment Change- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
